lead_paragraph: Stephen Curry scored as many points as Utah's starting five combined. Yet it sure didn't look pretty early for the star-studded Warriors, who eventually found their groove in another lopsided result.

headline.print_headline: Curry, Warriors Warm Up and Thump Utah Jazz 104-74
